reviewText: Very amaterish and I wouldn't recommend it to anyone. Cheap production values and a dull, DVD to watch. I tossed it out. Bought it on Amazon. Cover looked interesting.

This video is not of good quality and the acting, if you can call it that is terrible.  After an initial viewing, I will probably donate this to someone or someplace, maybe the garbage.  Don't waste your time or money.

Great premise - backstage at a strip club, with the new guys being all nervous about stripping on stage!  Natural guy next door types, no fake tan drugged up gogo dancers like at the bars.

Thanks for this fun vid.
